single.mph is the base model we use to train
bitmaptrans.m is a programe which can turn bitmaps into comsol models and simulate them
bitmapbuild.m is how we chose 5000 different samples
bitmap_to_simVer2.m is programmed to simulate different samples which bitmapbuild.m had generated
